    "description": "Little Keepers is an indie chaotic couch-coop tower defense that will put your friendship to test!<br><br>Mom has been doing experiments in our garden and now the plants are attacking us! As the Little Keepers, you’ll be given the chance to gather resources, build your defenses and create the best strategy to defend your home from spooky creatures. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2378390/extras/10fab1bf19be840be9094c673ea7130f.avif?t=1763422622\" width=610 height=140 /></span><br>You and your partner in crime, hand in hand against cute spooky hordes... Good Ol’ Couch Coop.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2378390/extras/44a2ac9781a53eb9aa69895310e9ba88.poster.avif?t=1763422622\" width=600 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2378390/extras/44a2ac9781a53eb9aa69895310e9ba88.webm?t=1763422622\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2378390/extras/44a2ac9781a53eb9aa69895310e9ba88.mp4?t=1763422622\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2378390/extras/90464697b4e3444e0f821d7741c20095.avif?t=1763422622\" width=610 height=140 /></span><br>Collect materials throughout the map and choose between metal or wood to give life to your creations! BUT BEWARE, some resources are too heavy to carry alone… the two of you must team up to carry them.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2378390/extras/b971d4c51742ea5dd221a15cabec1c17.poster.avif?t=1763422622\" width=600 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2378390/extras/b971d4c51742ea5dd221a15cabec1c17.webm?t=1763422622\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2378390/extras/b971d4c51742ea5dd221a15cabec1c17.mp4?t=1763422622\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2378390/extras/6d43faa303e39e37a47d850dbeb782dd.avif?t=1763422622\" width=610 height=140 /></span><br>Enjoy a balanced system with multiple options to complete levels and a difficulty curve worthy of the best strategists. In Little Keepers each game is different, and each strategy is as unique as its creator.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2378390/extras/ff4330a3014bf1c94f06f174d6c3b5ad.poster.avif?t=1763422622\" width=600 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2378390/extras/ff4330a3014bf1c94f06f174d6c3b5ad.webm?t=1763422622\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2378390/extras/ff4330a3014bf1c94f06f174d6c3b5ad.mp4?t=1763422622\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2378390/extras/3a90f2d0bcd486999beed5f55a569f08.avif?t=1763422622\" width=610 height=140 /></span><br>It won't matter if you and your buddy work together as synchronized as a Swiss clock... CHAOS IS INEVITABLE! (But it's also funny so enjoy!)<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2378390/extras/84234e81dc4d2fb06b2f33d2fd39bb5b.poster.avif?t=1763422622\" width=600 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2378390/extras/84234e81dc4d2fb06b2f33d2fd39bb5b.webm?t=1763422622\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2378390/extras/84234e81dc4d2fb06b2f33d2fd39bb5b.mp4?t=1763422622\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2378390/extras/70c1efeee1d7eae2ab1f092f00d82453.avif?t=1763422622\" width=610 height=140 /></span><br>Step into a cute &amp; spooky wonderworld and face together the monsters that shelter the forest.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2378390/extras/1f6070471931264694ba489937a3a413.poster.avif?t=1763422622\" width=610 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2378390/extras/1f6070471931264694ba489937a3a413.webm?t=1763422622\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2378390/extras/1f6070471931264694ba489937a3a413.mp4?t=1763422622\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2378390/extras/86baa186388cde326630176d3a45d5f8.avif?t=1763422622\" width=610 height=140 /></span><br>For the loners… you are not alone! Little AI will be by your side in good and bad (but mostly good, really, it’s extremely efficient!)<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2378390/extras/aa89e79b6b1d5ec6af0ef77dde0bd7e6.poster.avif?t=1763422622\" width=600 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2378390/extras/aa89e79b6b1d5ec6af0ef77dde0bd7e6.webm?t=1763422622\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2378390/extras/aa89e79b6b1d5ec6af0ef77dde0bd7e6.mp4?t=1763422622\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
